, \"rank\": 0.027972027972036382, \"text\": \"Zhang Yufei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yufei_(swimmer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the silver and bronze medals\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alonso went on to announce her shock retirement from swimming at the age of just 20, thanking the sport for allowing her to 'dream' and live out her 'best experiences'.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alonso\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"her shock retirement\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"her 'best experiences\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Swimming: thank you for allowing me to dream, you taught me to fight, to try, perseverance, sacrifice, discipline and many more,' she wrote on her Instagram page.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.647842571082283e-22, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I gave you part of my life and I do not change it for anything in the world because I lived the best experiences of my life, you gave me thousands of joys, friends from other countries that I will always carry them in my heart, unique opportunities.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 864}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", 