guay\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\"}, {\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larissa Schaerer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larissa_Schaerer\"}, {\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\", \"score\": 0.9914777739480097, \"rank\": 0.008513857939533166, \"text\": \"COP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conference_of_the_parties\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her presence\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"an inappropriate atmosphere\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We thank her for proceeding as instructed, as it was of her own free will that she did not spend the night in the athletes' village.'\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"proceeding\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"her own free will\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reports at the time claimed Paraguayan Olympic chiefs were furious after Alonso allegedly snuck out of the athletes' village without permission to visit Disneyland Paris.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay\", \"score\": 0.9963655709969677, \"rank\": 0.0036469443306553486, \"text\": \"Paraguayan\"