 \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I made the decision to stop and I am happy that my last race will be at the Olympics,' she said.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"my last race\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2518}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am going to go to study in the United States, I am going to continue my career in political science and, why not, be sports minister one day.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2590, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996947308875407, \"rank\": 0.0002993526080227726, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"political science\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"sports minister\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will always have a fondness for swimming and I may attend a competition, but it is not what I want in life.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fondness\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'What I want is to work for a company, I already have my life plan and hopefully it can happen.'\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a company\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"my life plan\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paraguayan also apologised for her performance in Paris, which came three years after her Olympic debut at t